headline: Revolution Medicines (RVMD): Assessing Valuation After Truist Highlights Potential of RAS-mutant Cancer Pipeline
summary: Revolution Medicines (RVMD) is turning heads this week after Truist initiated coverage with a Buy rating, spotlighting the company’s cutting-edge focus on RAS-mutant cancer therapies.
